title: Democratic Primary: Clinton Obama and Edwards Voting Results, New Hampshire, 2008
name: Democratic Primary: Clinton Obama and Edwards Voting Results, New Hampshire, 2008
description: The map is based on 95% or more precinct returns in the New Hampshire Democratic primary in 2008. The data consists of votes for individual candidates that were scraped, tabulated and geocoded for the three major Democratic candidates, Hillary who won the primary (39%), Obama (37%) and Edwards (13%).
